[Category "Competitive Bidding"]
[Difficulty "intermediate"]
[SkillPath "competitive_bidding/support_cuebids"]
[Student "S"]
{Partner has a limit raise or better  in \Ss, 11 points or more. 

There is only one thing you want to know now - how many Aces partner holds. So you bid 4NT to find out. Partner responds 5\H.  

You know you have a loser. Bid 6\S. }

